===Etymology===
From {{etyl|frm|en}} {{term|democratie|lang=frm}} (French {{term|démocratie|lang=fr}}) < {{ML.}} {{term|democratia|lang=la}} < {{etyl|grc|en}} {{term|δημοκράτια|tr=dēmokratia|lang=grc|sc=polytonic}}.  The Greek word in turn was formed from {{term|δῆμος||common people|tr=dēmos|lang=grc|sc=polytonic}} + {{term|κράτος||rule, strength|tr=kratos|lang=grc|sc=polytonic}}.

===Pronunciation===
